      <title>悉尼赌场第二次调查后，澳大利亚星娱乐公司股价跌至历史新低</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/australias-star-entertainment-hits-record-low-second-inquiry-into-sydney-casino-2024-02-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，澳大利亚明星娱乐集团 (Star Entertainment Group) 的股价暴跌近 26%，创历史新低，一天前新南威尔士州赌场监管机构表示将对该公司在悉尼的赌场业务进行第二次调查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/australias-star-entertainment-hits-record-low-second-inquiry-into-sydney-casino-2024-02-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 00:54:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管通胀有所缓和，韩国央行仍将维持政策利率不变直至第三季度</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/bok-keep-policy-rate-unchanged-until-q3-despite-easing-inflation-2024-02-20/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社调查的所有经济学家均表示，韩国央行将于 2 月 22 日连续第九次会议维持关键政策利率不变，他们坚持长期以来的观点，首次降息将在第三季度进行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/bok-keep-policy-rate-unchanged-until-q3-despite-easing-inflation-2024-02-20/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 20 Feb 2024 00:52:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
