      <title>墨西哥总体通胀二月初放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/mexican-headline-inflation-seen-slowing-early-february-2024-02-19/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[路透社周一的一项民意调查显示，墨西哥的总体通胀率可能在 2 月上半月有所放缓，这增强了对该国央行可能很快自 2021 年以来首次降低关键基准利率的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/mexican-headline-inflation-seen-slowing-early-february-2024-02-19/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 19:16:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
