      <title>据天空新闻报道，美国投资者正在与 Superdry 联合创始人就收购该连锁店进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/us-investor-talks-with-superdry-co-founder-about-bid-chain-sky-news-reports-2024-02-19/</link>
